title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Fantasy 5' game
maintext:
TALLAHASSEE, Fla. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Florida Lottery’s “Fantasy 5” game were:
02-13-25-32-33
(two, thirteen, twenty-five, thirty-two, thirty-three)
